{"id": "art-5811", "label": "Art. 5811", "title": "Art. 5811: Anularea renunţării la aplicarea pedepsei", "slug": "art-5811", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_127306187\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1128\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_127306187\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 581<sup>1</sup>:\nAnularea renun&#355;&#259;rii la aplicarea pedepsei </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1357662665\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1127\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1357662665\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Anularea renun&#355;&#259;rii la aplicarea pedepsei se\ndispune, din oficiu sau la sesizarea procurorului, de instan&#355;a care\njudec&#259; ori a judecat în prim&#259; instan&#355;&#259; infrac&#355;iunea ce\natrage anularea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_459901427\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1126\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_459901427\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; constat&#259; c&#259; sunt îndeplinite\ncondi&#355;iile art. 82 alin. (3) din </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul\npenal</span><span style='color:black'>, instan&#355;a, anulând renun&#355;area\nla aplicarea pedepsei, dispune condamnarea inculpatului pentru\ninfrac&#355;iunea cu privire la care se renun&#355;ase la aplicarea pedepsei,\nstabile&#351;te pedeapsa pentru aceasta, aplicând apoi, dup&#259; caz, dispozi&#355;iile\ncu privire la concursul de infrac&#355;iuni, recidiv&#259; sau pluralitate\nintermediar&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1089900469\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1125\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1089900469\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)La stabilirea pedepsei pentru infrac&#355;iunea cu\nprivire la care se anuleaz&#259; renun&#355;area la aplicarea pedepsei,\ninstan&#355;a va avea în vedere exclusiv criteriile de individualizare &#351;i\ncircumstan&#355;ele din cauza în care s-a pronun&#355;at ini&#355;ial\nsolu&#355;ia de renun&#355;are la aplicarea pedepsei. Dispozi&#355;iile art.\n396 alin. (10) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>"}